		 * the current band and the next one. band n and n+1 shouldn't touch.
		 *
		 * ==============================================================
		 *                                                        band n
		 *            +------+                    +------+
		 * ===========| rect |====================|      |===============
		 *            |      |    +------+        |      |
		 *            +------+    | rect |        | rect |
		 *                        +------+        |      |
		 * =======================================|      |================
		 *                                        +------+         band n+1
		 * ===============================================================
		 *
		 */
